## Server runtime artefacts (never commit these).
## Note: the literal lowercase folder name `data/` was matching the source
## namespace folder `Data/` too because git on Windows runs with
## core.ignorecase=true. We list the specific runtime files instead.
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/data/chat.db*
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/data/attachments/
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/data/avatars/
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/logs/
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/certs/
src/EnterpriseChat.Server/plugins/
